By: Swâmi Brahmânanda
---
Never forget the ideal of human life. ... Since it has been given you
to attain human birth, reject all the pleasures of the world. Be
firmly resolved to realize God and attain infinite felicity. Do not
give in, even if you have to die in this effort.
